EMMA S. MOORE v. WILTON FLOYD ALMON 17 So. (2nd) 123

January Term, 1944

February 25, 1944 Division A E. M. Baynes, for appellant. No appearance for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The judgment appealed from is reversed upon authority of Di Giorgio v. Di Giorgio, 153 Fla. 24, 12 So. (2nd) 596, and Dorman v. Friendly, 146 Fla. 732, 1 So. (2nd) 734.

*202Reversed.

BUFORD, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and ADAMS, JJ., concur. _
